<p>
<table border=0 width="90%"><tr><td nowrap bgcolor="#EEEEEE"><pre>
  ok <b>probe-scsi</b>

  Target 0
    Unit 0   Disk     QUANTUM LIGHTNING 365S
  Target 1
    Unit 0   Removable Disk     QUANTUM EMPIRE_1080S
